==English==
===Noun===
'''Nemesis''' (plural: [[nemeses]])
#The [[goddess]] of [[divine]] [[retribution]] and [[vengeance]] (always capitalized)
#The polar opposite of a character
#an arch enemy
#*"Batman is in constant conflict with his '''nemesis''', The Joker." 
#In the video game, 'resident evil 3', the main enemy is actually called Nemesis.
#The righteous infliction of retribution manifested by an appropriate agent.
#Nemesis was the name of a "rogue moon" in [[Sailor Moon]] [[manga]] and [[anime]] series.
